  "original_title": "\u0b95\u0bc1\u0b9f\u0bbf\u0bb5\u0bb0\u0bb5\u0bc1, \u0b95\u0bc1\u0b9f\u0bbf\u0baf\u0b95\u0bb2\u0bcd\u0bb5\u0bc1 \u0ba4\u0bbf\u0ba3\u0bc8\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0bae\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbf\u0baf \u0ba8\u0b9f\u0bb5\u0b9f\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc8",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "A major activity of the Department of Immigration and Emigration",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Sub-offices of the Department of Immigration and Emigration will be established immediately in all district secretariats of the country.",
        "According to this, it is mentioned that arrangements are being made to provide space in the district secretariats for setting up sub-offices of the Department of Immigration and Emigration.",
        "It has been pointed out that sub-offices are being established in order to reduce the congestion in the Pattaramullai main office. (a)"
      ],
